WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.400
The government's master plan: a committee

00:00:02.400 --> 00:00:04.800
to form committees about committees. Good

00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:07.200
evening. The government has unveiled its

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:09.600
master plan. A committee to form

00:00:09.600 --> 00:00:12.000
a committee about committees. (Cutaway -

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.400
Stewie-style minister in a lavish room)

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:16.800
Gentlemen, I propose we form a

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:19.200
sub-committee. To discuss the forming of

00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:21.600
further committees. (Room full of identical

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:24.000
officials nod vigorously) In related news,

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:26.400
the Committee Committee has formed a

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:28.800
Committee Committee Committee. (Organizational chart explodes.

00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:31.200
Persian text: 'کمیته‌های بی‌نهایت') Follow for

00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:31.600
more!

